{"tid":2035516,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黑田東彥料日本經濟持續嚴峻 必要時放寬政策","createTime":"2020-05-26T03:15:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T07:10:34.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"22f8100d577fabc14e4fa132ff2e8006771566f2","tid":2035516,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T03:15:29.000Z","msg":"黑田東彥料日本經濟持續嚴峻 必要時放寬政策<br />\n2020-05-26 HKT 11:07<br />\n<br />\n日本央行總裁黑田東彥表示，受新型肺炎疫情影響，日本經濟將持續嚴峻，物價仍然疲弱雖然政府解除全面緊急狀態，但維持對經濟低迷的看法，經濟前景風險偏向下行。<br />\n<br />\n他重申，央行將關注疫情的影響，必要時將毫不遲疑地放寬政策，並與政府配合，積極採取措施以紓緩企業壓力。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，必要時央行能進一步擴大信貸計劃規模及調整利率目標，但央行難以直接承擔金融機構因疫情所致的貸款壞帳損失。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1528369-20200526.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1528369-20200526.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjYz44BXU%2FO%2BPkTPvsbUsuc1I%3D&h=1005e966\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1528369-20200526.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=60c2737d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1528369-20200526.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我非常肯定重新容許香港人到日本旅遊能大力振興日本經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"2a6b88ee1d694d0de7de88727a4b40d7dc6eaa34","tid":2035516,"uid":259716,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T07:10:34.000Z","msg":"極度掛住日本。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}